    <abstract id="aspace_019971ab6345b69ef04eaa742317f86c">The Brian Purnell civil rights in Brooklyn research collection includes Dr. Purnell's research notes and photocopies of archival materials held at Center for Brooklyn History and other institutions related to the Brooklyn chapters of the National Association for the Advancement of Colored People and the Congress of Racial Equality.</abstract>
